812
01:24:07,060 --> 01:24:10,920
[SPEAKER_01] Velika zahvala i lasti.

813
01:24:10,920 --> 01:24:12,380
[SPEAKER_01] Keksu,

814
01:24:12,380 --> 01:24:14,779
